OL,3,CUK police probing allegations of child
OL,4,Csexual abuse after Epstein files
OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FSurrey Police is investigating two
OL,8,Fseparate allegations of non-recent
OL,9,Fchild sexual abuse following the
OL,10,Frelease of files related to paedophile
OL,11,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,13,FSurrey Police said it was probing one
OL,14,Freport from locations in Surrey and
OL,15,FBerkshire in the mid-1990s to 2000 and
OL,16,Fa separate allegation from the mid to
OL,17,Flate 1980s in West Surrey.
OL,19,FThe force said no arrests have been
OL,20,Fmade.
