PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779279069
OL,3,CUK police probing allegations of child
OL,4,Csexual abuse after Epstein files
OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FSurrey Police have followed separate
OL,8,Finvestigations by Thames Valley Police
OL,9,Fand the Metropolitan Police, who have
OL,10,Farrested Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor
OL,11,Fand Lord Peter Mandelson respectively
OL,12,Ffor alleged misconduct in public
OL,13,Foffice.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Surrey Police said:
OL,16,F"Following the release offiles
OL,17,Frelating to Jeffrey Epsteinby the US
OL,18,Fdepartment of justice, we are
OL,19,Finvestigating two separate allegations
OL,20,Fof non-recent child sexual abuse.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
