PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779279069
OL,3,CUK police probing allegations of child
OL,4,Csexual abuse after Epstein files
OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,F"One report relates to locations in
OL,8,FSurrey and Berkshire in the mid-1990s
OL,9,Fto 2000. The other relates to the mid-
OL,10,Fto-late 1980s in West Surrey.
OL,12,F"No arrests have been made.
OL,14,F"We take all reports of sexual
OL,15,Foffending seriously and will work to
OL,16,Fidentify any reasonable lines of
OL,17,Finquiry to verify information or
OL,18,Festablish corroborating evidence."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@AOUzD@bO]
